                <note rend="inline" type="source">711.21/668: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Colombia</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Philip</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Bogotá</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1921-12-24T18:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 24, 1921—6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received December 26—10:50 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>64. My 61 of December 22, 5 p.m.<note n="10" xml:id="d613fn10">Not
                        printed.</note> Law number 56 approving modifications introduced by the U.S.
                    in the treaty of April 6, 1914, <pb facs="0769" n="645" xml:id="pg_645"/> was
                    signed by Executive and Minister for Foreign Affairs today, the 24th
                        instant.<note n="11" xml:id="d613fn11">The modified treaty was presented to
                        the Colombian Congress Aug. 20, 1921, and approved by it on Dec. 22.</note>
                    Article 2 of this law is embodied in Spanish text of enclosure number 3 with my
                    despatch number 727 of October 17 last<note n="12" xml:id="d613fn12">Not
                        printed.</note> and I request that Department delay preparation of our
                    exchange copy of ratification pending my further consultation with Colombian
                    authorities.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Philip</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
